<L>__{interior barracks night}
<A>__{mother and daughter enter their crude quarters. they find hatsue's sisters sitting on the wooden floor, watching... ...a team of young men, working with tools and pieces of lumber. one is building shelves, two others, a chest of drawers. their leader kneels tacking scraps of tin over the knotholes on the floor. one girl beams at her mother...}
<C>__{sumiko}
<D>__{these boys are buildings us a mansion!}
<A>__{the leader grins and rises. bows slightly to fujiko. he is, of course...}
